{"tid":660562,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「告別之前，我會向每一棵樹道別。」","createTime":"2018-05-10T19:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T09:06:04.000Z","uid":165817,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"21ec7bafe2078fdb61e78ee66a19a28f627c366e","tid":660562,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T19:22:09.000Z","msg":"「訓練基地外有兩萬棵樹。我來的時候，他們還是小小的樹苗，而如今，他們都已經成為了參天大樹。告別之前，我會向每一棵樹道別，並向它們說聲：『謝謝。』」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/032146_f6a523ae122ff9ba7c017716e8766d2a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F032146_f6a523ae122ff9ba7c017716e8766d2a.jpeg&h=e04490fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7564831270add38f1a3e1066f642b96284681b21","tid":660562,"uid":143768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T19:44:06.000Z","msg":"想咸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60eca78724dfa02cb152f0714916853346fc7362","tid":660562,"uid":77880,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T20:06:17.000Z","msg":"唔洗客氣"},{"pid":"16cdb90980d7b134a61bf21092ccd795afe0efa4","tid":660562,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T21:28:05.000Z","msg":"作客其他球隊時，人地領隊總是都多謝我。🤔"},{"pid":"df8c79401526743a89a1851afa0235ddc7f08602","tid":660562,"uid":86413,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T22:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pics.me.me/us-emirates-stadium-save-er-www-facebook-com-justtoonit-savewenger-%E0%B8%96%E0%B8%B6%E0%B8%87%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%B8%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%9E%E0%B8%B7%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%88%E0%B9%8A%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%81%E0%B9%82%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%87%E0%B9%81%E0%B8%A5%E0%B9%89%E0%B